# plc_or_device_tool Profile

## Purpose

Use this profile for PLC, device, equipment, or hardware-adjacent tools where live side effects can be high risk.

## Safety Position

- Simulator/mock first.
- Read-only polling before any write concept.
- Live device write is prohibited by default.
- Equipment IP, port, tag, address, and live parameter details must not be committed.

## Recommended Work Before Implementation

- Define product and MVP contracts.
- Define simulator/mock assumptions.
- Define read-only polling boundaries.
- Define safety and verification evidence.
- Define explicit approval requirements for any future live action.

## P1 Boundary

This profile template does not create real device connections, PLC logic, configs, or equipment scripts.
